==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[zenial]] [[passage]]}}

# The [[pass]]ing of the [[sun]] [[directly]] [[overhead]] such that no [[shadow]]s are cast by a pole sticking straight up from the ground.  These conditions only occur in locations between the [[Tropic of Cancer]] and the [[Tropic of Capricorn]].  

===Trivia===
Zenial passages were important to the [[Maya]] civilization.

